Class ElementStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sebuilder.interpreter.steptype.ElementStyle
      • org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib.interpreter.selrunner.steptype.ElementStyle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.sebuilder.interpreter.Getter, SRunnerType

    public class ElementStyle
extends com.sebuilder.interpreter.steptype.ElementStyle
implements SRunnerType
    Author:
    Lei Wang This a getter class for get element's css style, its parameters are:
    parameter[0] the command itself, such as storeElementStyle, verifyElementStyle etc.
    parameter[1] the element locator.
    parameter[2] the element's css style name.
    parameter[3] the variable name (if the command begins with store); the value to compare (if the command begins with verify).
